{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/redirectStart","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Resource_Timing_API\">Resource Timing API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming\"><code>PerformanceResourceTiming</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/connectEnd\"><code>connectEnd</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/connectStart\"><code>connectStart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/decodedBodySize\"><code>decodedBodySize</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/domainLookupEnd\"><code>domainLookupEnd</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/domainLookupStart\"><code>domainLookupStart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/encodedBodySize\"><code>encodedBodySize</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/fetchStart\"><code>fetchStart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/initiatorType\"><code>initiatorType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/nextHopProtocol\"><code>nextHopProtocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/redirectEnd\"><code>redirectEnd</code></a></li><li><em><code>redirectStart</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/requestStart\"><code>requestStart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/responseEnd\"><code>responseEnd</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/responseStart\"><code>responseStart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/secureConnectionStart\"><code>secureConnectionStart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/serverTiming\"><code>serverTiming</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/transferSize\"><code>transferSize</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/workerStart\"><code>workerStart</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/toJSON\"><code>toJSON()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceEntry\"><code>PerformanceEntry</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Resource Timing API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceEntry\"><code>PerformanceEntry</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>performance_property</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>redirectStart</code></strong> read-only property returns a\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\" title=\"timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a> representing the start time of the fetch\n  which that initiates the redirect.\n</p>\n<p>\n  If there are HTTP redirects when fetching the resource and if any of the redirects are\n  not from the same origin as the current document, but the timing allow check algorithm\n  passes for each redirected resource, this property returns the starting time of the\n  fetch that initiates the redirect; otherwise, zero is returned.\n</p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\" title=\"timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a> representing the start time of the\n  fetch which initiates the redirect.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  In the following example, the value of the <code>*Start</code> and <code>*End</code>\n  properties of all \"<code>resource</code>\"\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceEntry/entryType\" title=\"type\"><code>type</code></a> events are logged.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">print_PerformanceEntries</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Use getEntriesByType() to just get the \"resource\" events</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> performance<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getEntriesByType</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"resource\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">print_start_and_end_properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">print_start_and_end_properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">perfEntry</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Print timestamps of the PerformanceEntry *start and *end properties</span>\n  properties <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"connectStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"connectEnd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"domainLookupStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"domainLookupEnd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"fetchStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"redirectStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"redirectEnd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"requestStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"responseStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"responseEnd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"secureConnectionStart\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> properties<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// check each property</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> perfEntry<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>properties<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>properties<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> perfEntry<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"… \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> properties<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" = \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"… \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> properties<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\" = NOT supported\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/resource-timing/#dom-performanceresourcetiming-redirectstart","title":"Resource Timing Level 2"}],"query":"api.PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/redirectStart/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The redirectStart read-only property returns a\n  timestamp representing the start time of the fetch\n  which that initiates the redirect.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-17T06:18:04.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/performanceresourcetiming/redirectstart","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/performanceresourcetiming/redirectstart/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/db5398504f193f4a285b170ec8ad87f816257b4e","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming","title":"PerformanceResourceTiming"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/redirectStart","title":"PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart"}],"pageTitle":"PerformanceResourceTiming.redirectStart - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}